{"tid":28830,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［貓奴］入黎討論下自己主人","createTime":"2016-12-08T07:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T19:11:59.000Z","uid":58463,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84b4c5af53aeff08fad66061f46991164b057aa9","tid":28830,"uid":58463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:41:53.000Z","msg":"［貓奴］入黎討論下自己主人"},{"pid":"5a06b6a17db20bcfddbf147df81f21d6f191dedb","tid":28830,"uid":31745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:09:22.000Z","msg":"有一隻行為似狗既貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162197793f5986e3817624576ea5163f2a7d53e3","tid":28830,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有一隻行為似狗既貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nX2"},{"pid":"15b8a0578284705d6a6093603b59edd393649ff2","tid":28830,"uid":39174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有一隻行為似狗既貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nX2</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 屋企唔俾養"},{"pid":"d58cbf1d78f8bff0cc312644b8eab879117133d7","tid":28830,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"成日望街 成日咬我 見到人會show個肚腩畀人睇"},{"pid":"8865d5fc0ae99faa1c9f63e34241200e0d9b8f4a","tid":28830,"uid":28948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:55:24.000Z","msg":"我成日好擔心主人，佢已經12歲，係肥仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好驚佢突然會走...有時電話響都驚係屋企人打黎報壞消息，返工/唔係屋企嘅日子都會凝住會有事發生，又成日發惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a705aa3c2e0a9c1a3e7c3de5f062d40655f2031","tid":28830,"uid":14219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:58:08.000Z","msg":"成日扭我耳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7fbdfa3f827698638d4b09b043c45e09fe383a","tid":28830,"uid":59612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:07:43.000Z","msg":"成日好似狗咁看門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到腳步聲即刻走去門口睇"},{"pid":"ffe417d4501ab3b93373dcea046cda7e0374e6b9","tid":28830,"uid":45526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有一隻行為似狗既貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nX2</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nX3"},{"pid":"5f4c5a264be94d3fecc7b649be4b1c0c07034547","tid":28830,"uid":12855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日好似狗咁看門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到腳步聲即刻走去門口睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來唔止我主人係禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁貪玩，好中意岀街溝女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ded4cd4caa1de6f82fee9356309d54730a6a04a","tid":28830,"uid":31540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"冇圖都有討論價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2a777320f71da6a856637575e9fc614f0afd6a","tid":28830,"uid":59709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成日好擔心主人，佢已經12歲，係肥仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好驚佢突然會走...有時電話響都驚係屋企人打黎報壞消息，返工/唔係屋企嘅日子都會凝住會有事發生，又成日發惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個隻都好大年紀少肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前暑假去exchange好驚最後一面都無得見<br />\n還好而家仲行得訓得<br />\n但晚餐食少左，中意食既貓零食都唔太食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係屋企第一隻貓，想像唔到無左佢煩我會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0ac5e63eb6eace0680a7d7ea76a83dc8f64190","tid":28830,"uid":28948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我成日好擔心主人，佢已經12歲，係肥仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好驚佢突然會走...有時電話響都驚係屋企人打黎報壞消息，返工/唔係屋企嘅日子都會凝住會有事發生，又成日發惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個隻都好大年紀少肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前暑假去exchange好驚最後一面都無得見<br />\n還好而家仲行得訓得<br />\n但晚餐食少左，中意食既貓零食都唔太食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係屋企第一隻貓，想像唔到無左佢煩我會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老左淨係識得食同訓就更加肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲可以分享方法，令老貓肯郁多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c55c6865d52317b6ce1c5ae05e12e517bc49a1","tid":28830,"uid":58855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"我主人都係12歲<br />\n全日行得最快嘅時間就係開飯果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db13daae7b207defb1ca5871af196a98d1157ee8","tid":28830,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有一隻行為似狗既貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nX2</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nx3"},{"pid":"c2ea4dd56e0c7253bdda6340ef09fe88d025059b","tid":28830,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:06:44.000Z","msg":"感情好好 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7u70aFT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7u70aFT.jpg&h=3664e953&s={SIZE}\" />但一男一女好怕搞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce76dbe8c579376feec27b5e4ff7332de6eb4f27","tid":28830,"uid":28948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:39:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感情好好 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7u70aFT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7u70aFT.jpg&h=3664e953&s={SIZE}\" />但一男一女好怕搞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕就幫佢地絕育啦"},{"pid":"798fcafdba6d8699256a5a9fe45a19e784f739f4","tid":28830,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:52:47.000Z","msg":"永冇完美<br />\n發情期主動任人摸任人抱 捉實你隻手要你摸佢<br />\n見到你行即行去前邊要你摸 嗲到痴線<br />\n但晚晚凌晨叫春 叫聲重要似虐待緊佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係發情期 唔會叫 成日要玩<br />\n但唔比抱 一抱即鬧你咬你 照住你來咬<br />\n最重要係 會無啦啦搵你隻揪 <br />\n訓係到睇緊電視 冇啦啦衝過來拍你一下頭 之後走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea2b4fb514d19d8983489d9283fd5f16bbbfd0c","tid":28830,"uid":59219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:57:10.000Z","msg":"主人以前朝朝早6點半會係咁喵我叫我起身返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3fe5643cba718d9cbbd8acdf73004b827eb6bbf","tid":28830,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>感情好好 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7u70aFT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7u70aFT.jpg&h=3664e953&s={SIZE}\" />但一男一女好怕搞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕就幫佢地絕育啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbook左下星期16號絕<br />\n老實說 得3個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c534c6a0706ac6bdfe30477229c5921cea1293","tid":28830,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:02:11.000Z","msg":"從貓既行為分出幾個佢點睇D奴隸(我隻貓)<br />\n奴隸級: <br />\n貓會成隻狗咁跟出跟入,連柯屎都想入去一齊果種<br />\n發出呼嚕嚕聲少不免.唔係呢個級別既人係聽唔到<br />\n唔知點解識聲腳步聲,一開門就喵你<br />\n會訓你張床.基本上就係好似係佢自己咁自出自入<br />\n<br />\n餵食級:<br />\n冇呼嚕嚕聲.冇跟出跟入.見到你都想叫你行開<br />\n知你想捉佢一定匿撚埋.除非都比你捉實佢先勉為其難比你抱下<br />\n基本上就係當你路人.有零食就敷衍下你. 我就係呢個級別<br />\n但有時我可以聽到呼嚕嚕聲(覺得自己同其他屋企人唔同而自豪?)<br />\n<br />\n永不靠近級:<br />\n佢絕對唔比捉到唔比摸到.迫得太驚會FU人<br />\n有野食都唔會理你<br />\n<br />\n相處都有6年左右: 2-3歲領養<br />\n隻貓唔對你呼嚕,應該係冇咩可能升級上去<br />\n但可以從永不靠近級升上餵食級..到時就有雞脾食"},{"pid":"63986d2f06e6429e6479183828fb963abbfc5a4f","tid":28830,"uid":52421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:06:04.000Z","msg":"極度痴人 可能以前比人遺棄過  會跟出跟入 瞓交果陣佢唔見屋企人會狂喵 養多隻陪佢之後情況好左好多"},{"pid":"f848778b9f83b14c02351c5808acd3935255faf5","tid":28830,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"傲嬌主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋成日擔住d 玩具行黎行去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oriNQn5E6WIeO5ouA/200w.gif \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oriNQn5E6WIeO5ouA%2F200w.gif%20&h=82aeb44c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1a784c04e0f3b310096b000b74995f05723d7bd","tid":28830,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:17:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我主人都係12歲<br />\n全日行得最快嘅時間就係開飯果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑左<br />\n但可以陪你咁耐 真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa7cadbbb5b528b881f2897d5fd1ab823504451","tid":28830,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從貓既行為分出幾個佢點睇D奴隸(我隻貓)<br />\n奴隸級: <br />\n貓會成隻狗咁跟出跟入,連柯屎都想入去一齊果種<br />\n發出呼嚕嚕聲少不免.唔係呢個級別既人係聽唔到<br />\n唔知點解識聲腳步聲,一開門就喵你<br />\n會訓你張床.基本上就係好似係佢自己咁自出自入<br />\n<br />\n餵食級:<br />\n冇呼嚕嚕聲.冇跟出跟入.見到你都想叫你行開<br />\n知你想捉佢一定匿撚埋.除非都比你捉實佢先勉為其難比你抱下<br />\n基本上就係當你路人.有零食就敷衍下你. 我就係呢個級別<br />\n但有時我可以聽到呼嚕嚕聲(覺得自己同其他屋企人唔同而自豪?)<br />\n<br />\n永不靠近級:<br />\n佢絕對唔比捉到唔比摸到.迫得太驚會FU人<br />\n有野食都唔會理你<br />\n<br />\n相處都有6年左右: 2-3歲領養<br />\n隻貓唔對你呼嚕,應該係冇咩可能升級上去<br />\n但可以從永不靠近級升上餵食級..到時就有雞脾食</blockquote><br />\n有無試過&quot;貓接吻&quot;?<br />\n同貓眼神接觸慢慢眨眼<br />\n我初初接貓翻屋企佢地好驚唔睬人<br />\n試左幾日而家反而覺得嗲過頭有啲煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申，接左個半月"},{"pid":"60b1f5aa386c1bf04a0c843b60bbb8148d745073","tid":28830,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:47:05.000Z","msg":"我隻野會咀我 又會lam我眉毛 勁咕嚕 但從來唔喵我 除非要我抱佢 因為我兩隻 如果淨係抱住一隻 另一隻會呷醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd37bcc734c9ea675cd3f06b1528a5a7e538dbe7","tid":28830,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>感情好好 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7u70aFT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7u70aFT.jpg&h=3664e953&s={SIZE}\" />但一男一女好怕搞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕就幫佢地絕育啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbook左下星期16號絕<br />\n老實說 得3個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁細個做好似唔係咁好喎 <br />\n全身麻醉風險好大架<br />\n可能佢都未必夠磅數做"},{"pid":"d31c871534c2ce04d850e67a10c252fe3edf49dc","tid":28830,"uid":10108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:56:21.000Z","msg":"我隻貓仔呢排係張床呀 被呀 cushion滴幾滴尿<br />\n早排轉凍拎左張棉被出黎 冚左兩日聞到勁臭壓味，原來屙左一大篤落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗完返黎幾日又有陣味，有幾滴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪要準備切蛋蛋喇？佢而家九個月大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a06d6875d018d2ad9ba9e8a114d4a0fe30b513","tid":28830,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/08/231240_c677e64ca532141b5cda82d3a6d39feb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F08%2F231240_c677e64ca532141b5cda82d3a6d39feb.jpg&h=2eea60bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港女格 熟既就係咁鬧你 行過都叫你埋去 唔識既見到都腳震<br />\n姐係好恰就恰到盡 惡過佢就做um 春<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6q9v0C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6q9v0C.jpg&h=78cc1b80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af47ff6d2d2c3bce72cfcd963f9bcae1bc406be0","tid":28830,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我主人都係12歲<br />\n全日行得最快嘅時間就係開飯果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde46a361c65b13e613607088d4176d0efe0d71f","tid":28830,"uid":22614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy